data.tab-panel#Tab Panel:
import { TabPanel } from 'funda-ui/Tabs';
Property	Type	Default	Description	Required	key	string | tab-panel-*	-	A “key” is a special string attribute you need to include when creating lists of elements. Let’s assign a key to our list of items. Must contain the string tab-panel	-	defaultActive	boolean	false	Set an item to activate by default	-	tabpanelClass	string	-	Additional style name, such as shadow	-	
It accepts all props(include data-* attributes) which native div support.

